==English==
===Noun===
'''aluminoxane'''
#{{chemistry}} a class of [[organometallic compound]]s of [[aluminium]] having [[general formula]] R<sub>2</sub>Al-O-AlR<sub>2</sub>; they are used as [[catalyst]]s in the [[polymerization]] of [[epoxide]]s and [[oxetane]]s to form [[polyether]] [[elastomer]]s
===Synonyms===
*[[Vandenburg catalyst]]

